data.value:
A Draw Geometry Shape is a GUI based program that allows the user to enter the certain text from the textbox as it defined in the program. Then it accepts the valid input from the user and draw respective shape i.e. circle, rectangle, triangle and a line.It Reads and executes commands on command line one at a time. Reads a program(in the program window) and executes it with a “run”. It identify Syntax Checks for valid commands and Checks for valid parameters. It reads the contents of files, scan these contents for certain shape patterns.
A 'User' or 'You' can select from Menu Items. Clear command to clear the drawing area reset command to move pen to initial position at top left of the screen. There are some pre-defined patterns in the program which comparesits shape according to the nature of files and shape parameter defined in the program.
